        <p>We are a community-driven store that offers a wide variety of gently used clothing, accessories.</p>
        <p>We promote sustainable living by providing an alternative to fast fashion and encouraging the reuse of clothes and other items.</p> 

        <p>We believe that everyone should have access to stylish and high-quality clothing and we are committed to making that happen.</p> 
         <p>So come visit us and see what treasures you can find!</p>
        </div>
        </div>

    )
}

export default About;
